channel.title: [C4D] Browning M1919
channel.description:
Ahh yes, more COD 5 weapons. The tank i will be re-doing and actually model it after a real tank rather than just using the blueprints for the body of it.
Right now, the browning is a bit basic. But alot better than how it was last night. Dont mind the pointless un-colored cylinder spot on the body of the gun.
The cloth is to keep the heated metal away from your bare hand if you didnt know.
[img]http://img68.imageshack.us/img68/236/browningzq0.png[/img]
